Cassini Installer Wizard Images
================================

Place branded images in this directory for the Inno Setup installer wizard.
These are optional — the installer works without them using Inno Setup defaults.

Required image specifications (Inno Setup 6, WizardStyle=modern):

  WizardImageFile (left panel on welcome/finish pages):
    - Filename: wizard-image.bmp
    - Dimensions: 164 x 314 pixels
    - Format: BMP (24-bit)

  WizardSmallImageFile (top-right corner on interior pages):
    - Filename: wizard-small-image.bmp
    - Dimensions: 55 x 55 pixels
    - Format: BMP (24-bit)

  SetupIconFile (setup .exe icon):
    - Already provided at ../backend/assets/cassini.ico
    - Format: ICO (multi-resolution: 16x16, 32x32, 48x48, 256x256)

To enable wizard images, add these lines to the [Setup] section in cassini.iss:

  WizardImageFile=assets\wizard-image.bmp
  WizardSmallImageFile=assets\wizard-small-image.bmp

Design guidance:
  - Use Saturnis brand colors and the Cassini logo
  - BMP format is required (Inno Setup does not accept PNG/JPG for wizard images)
  - The wizard image appears on a white/themed background — avoid hard edges
  - The small image should be a simple icon or logomark that reads well at 55x55
